<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Không tìm thấy trang</title>
    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      body { 
        background: #f4f4f4; 
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333; 
        display: flex; 
        align-items: center; 
        justify-content: center;
        height: 100vh; 
        text-align: center; 
        padding: 20px; 
      }
      .error-container {
        max-width: 500px; 
        background: white; 
        padding: 40px; 
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); 
        animation: slideIn 0.6s ease-out; 
      }
      .error-container h1 { 
        font-size: 72px; 
        color: #e74c3c;
        margin: 0; 
      }
      .error-container h2 { 
        font-size: 1.5rem; 
        margin: 10px 0 20px; 
        color: #333;
      }
      .error-container p { 
        font-size: 1rem; 
        margin-bottom: 20px; 
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #666;
      }
      .btn { 
        display: inline-block; 
        padding: 10px 20px; 
        background: #3498db; 
        color: white; 
        text-decoration: none; 
        border-radius: 4px; 
        transition: background 0.3s; 
      }
      .btn:hover { 
        background: #2980b9; 
      }
      @keyframes slideIn {
        from { 
          transform: translateY(30px); 
          opacity: 0; 
        }
        to { 
          transform: translateY(0); 
          opacity: 1; 
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="error-container">
      <h1>404</h1>
      <h2>Không tìm thấy trang</h2>
      <p>Trang bạn đang tìm kiếm không tồn tại hoặc đã bị di chuyển.</p>
      <a href="/" class="btn">Về trang chủ</a>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>